Statistics for this station calculated over all years of data

1) Calculation of statistics
Summary statistics, other than the Highest and Lowest values, are only calculated if there are at least 10 years of data available.
2) Gaps and missing data
Gaps may be caused by a damaged instrument, a temporary change to the site operation, or due to the absence or illness of an observer.
